==English==

===Etymology===
"Malé Islands", from [[Malé]], the name of the main island (of uncertain etymology), plus ''-diva, -dive'', "island", probably related to Sanskrit [[द्वीप]] (dvīpa) "island".

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}} {{p}}

# Country in [[South Asia]]. Official name: Republic of Maldives.

